[para]
[:en]
Subclause [#using] describes how a [=Cpp] program gains access to the facilities
of the [=Cpp] standard library.
[:zh_CN]
子条款 [#using] 描述 [=Cpp] 程序如何获得对 [=Cpp] 标准程序库的设施的访问。

[:en]
[#using.headers] describes effects during translation phase 4, while
[#using.linkage] describes effects during phase 8 ([#lex.phases]).
[:zh_CN]
[#using.headers] 描述翻译阶段 4 中的效果，而 [#using.linkage] 描述翻译阶段 8 中
的效果（[#lex.phases]）。
